# ozky — root .gitignore. Covers every sub-project's build/generated artifacts;
# the per-directory .gitignore files (contracts/, ozky/, web/, src-tauri/) still
# apply within their scopes. Cargo.lock / package-lock.json are intentionally
# tracked (apps + binaries) and are NOT ignored.

# ---- Rust / Cargo (contracts, indexer, ozky/src-tauri) ----
# Matches any `target/` dir at any depth — also catches Noir's circuit build output.
target/
**/*.rs.bk

# ---- Noir / Barretenberg (circuits/*/target: proof, vk, public_inputs, *.gz, *.json) ----
# Covered by the `target/` rule above; listed here for clarity.
# circuits/*/target/

# ---- Soroban ----
# Regenerable test snapshots from soroban-sdk tests.
**/test_snapshots/
# Local CLI state + deploy bookkeeping.
.soroban/
.stellar/
**/.contract_id

# ---- Node / SvelteKit (ozky/, web/) ----
node_modules/
.svelte-kit/
build/
dist/
.vercel/
vite.config.*.timestamp-*

# ---- Tauri generated ----
**/gen/schemas/

# ---- Secrets / local config (never commit) ----
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
# Local dev config holding deployed contract IDs + a relayer secret.
ozky.config.json

# ---- Logs / temp ----
*.log
*.tmp
tmp/

# ---- OS / editor cruft ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
#assets
*.stackdump
#*.md